### **4. 25_StreamSyncChart**  
**Description:**  
A responsive live chart that syncs with a real-time numeric data stream for visualization.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamSyncChart - Realtime Data Plotting Tool

StreamSyncChart turns real-time numeric input into a clean, scrollable chart for dashboards or metric analysis.

## Features
- Live line chart  
- Matplotlib-powered  
- Scrollable + auto-refresh  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_StreamSyncChart.git
cd 25_StreamSyncChart
python visualize.py
